ed="T" n="0758c26"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0758c26"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000011996">睦州龍興寺</placeName><persName key="A010151">慧朗</persName>傳（<persName key="A010154">𧦪<roleName>公</roleName></persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0758c27"/><persName key="A010151">釋慧朗</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000011974">新定遂安</placeName>人也。<date key="j19705211970885" from-iso="+0683-01-01" to-iso="+0683-12-31">年二十有二</date>，於<placeName key="PL000000013640">衢州<lb
ed="T" n="0758c28"/>北山</placeName>遇<ref type="person" target="#A001719">南宗頓教之首</ref>，將請為師，乃逆相<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1401"/><lb
ed="T" n="0758c29"/>謂曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010151">汝</ref>久積淨業，<ref type="person" target="#A001719">吾</ref>非<ref type="person" target="#A010151">汝</ref>師，可往<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>，當<pb ed="T" n="0759a" xml:id="T50.2061.0759a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0759a01"/>逢哲匠。」至<placeName key="PL000000013347">剡溪石城寺</placeName>見一禪翁，莫知<lb
ed="T" n="0759a02"/>其來，鶴髮氷膚，目如流電，聲含鍾律，神合<lb
ed="T" n="0759a03"/>太虛。乃問<persName key="A010151">朗</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010151">子</ref>將何之？」答曰：「欲往<placeName key="PL000000014411">天<lb
ed="T" n="0759a04"/>台</placeName>，求佛大法。」因同行十數里，憩林樹下，而<lb
ed="T" n="0759a05"/>指訓之曰：「法常寂然，彼亦如也。何必<anchor xml:id="beg0759001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>隨</sic><corr>適</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0759001"/>遠，<lb
ed="T" n="0759a06"/>當化有緣，宜歸本生，度無量眾。」言畢，求之<lb
ed="T" n="0759a07"/>無方，豁然本心悟佛知見，林棲谷飲，凡經<lb
ed="T" n="0759a08"/>數載，乃却歸故邑<placeName key="PL000000011936">慧安寺</placeName>。淨名白衣<ptr target="#n1367"/>，服非法<lb
ed="T" n="0759a09"/>服，<persName key="A017094">純陀</persName>工巧，心如佛心。驪珠<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1402"/>尚潛，師子未吼，<lb
ed="T" n="0759a10"/>弱喪<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1403"/>之終，涉川迷津。一日，<placeName key="PL000000013158">秦望山</placeName>林嶺振動，<lb
ed="T" n="0759a11"/>俄有大龜呈質<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1404"/>，咸相謂言：「此何祥也？」尋有<lb
ed="T" n="0759a12"/>禪僧<anchor xml:id="beg0759002"/>曰<anchor xml:id="end0759002"/>：「<persName key="A010154">𧦬</persName>自<placeName key="PL000000013295">會稽雲門</placeName>而來，身長八尺四<lb
ed="T" n="0759a13"/>寸，高鼻大目，睛光射人，明《大品》、《思益》、《維摩》等<lb
ed="T" n="0759a14"/>經，兼博通諸論。」眾曰：「神僧也，大龜應乎此<lb
ed="T" n="0759a15"/>也。」<persName key="A010151">朗</persName>祕菩薩行，請<ref type="person" target="#A010154">之</ref>為師。<persName key="A010154">𧦬</persName>徵《維摩經》義，<lb
ed="T" n="0759a16"/>答曰：「如日照螢火，海沃牛跡耳。」<persName key="A010154">𧦬<roleName>公</roleName></persName>深器<lb
ed="T" n="0759a17"/>之曰：「真淨名也。」<date notBefore-iso="+0707-10-09" key="j19795671980570" notAfter-iso="+0710-07-08">景龍中</date>，鄉人<placeName key="PL000000031004">吳川</placeName>縣尉<persName key="A010155">余少<lb
ed="T" n="0759a18"/>興</persName>、宗黨<placeName key="PL000000018717">新昌</placeName>縣令<persName key="A010156">余仁</persName>等十數家咸共宗事，<lb
ed="T" n="0759a19"/>遞請降臨。一夕，忽覩神光從項而出，旁燭<lb
ed="T" n="0759a20"/>山川，盈十數里，含情<ptr type="glossary" target="#g826"/>之類罔不歸依。<persName key="A010154">𧦬<roleName>公</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0759a21"/>加師資之禮，由茲反拜，請<persName key="A010151">朗</persName>登座。乃先示<lb
ed="T" n="0759a22"/>法身遍同群有<ptr type="glossary" target="#g826"/>，次明遍化一切皆如<ptr type="glossary" target="#g763"/>。道俗欣<lb
ed="T" n="0759a23"/>然而各歎曰：「昔山之震動，龜之斆祥，非<persName key="A010154">𧦬<roleName>公</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0759a24"/>之應，明矣。」至是四方學禪觀者臻萃<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1405"/>。<date from-iso="+0716-02-02" key="j19826051982988" to-iso="+0717-02-19">開元<lb
ed="T" n="0759a25"/>四年</date>，本州牧<persName key="A010158">李思絢</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000011985">龍山</placeName><ptr target="#n1368"/>之陽建伽藍<ptr target="#n1369"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0759a26"/>延以居之。方大設戒壇，廣邀律德，有<placeName key="PL000000025908">光州</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0759a27"/><persName key="A008876">岸<roleName>公</roleName></persName>、<placeName key="PL000000013240">會稽</placeName><persName key="A010159">超<roleName>公</roleName></persName>而為上首。既而發希有心，<lb
ed="T" n="0759a28"/>受具足戒，珠圓月滿，內外俱明，遍臨壇為<lb
ed="T" n="0759a29"/>戒師，旋請益為學士，眾情加重，道在益尊。<pb ed="T" n="0759b" xml:id="T50.2061.0759b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0759b01"/><date from-iso="+0719-01-30" key="j19836981984080" to-iso="+0720-02-16">七年</date>，刺史<persName key="A010161">韋利器</persName>深心歸向。<date from-iso="+0720-02-17" key="j19840811984434" to-iso="+0721-02-04">八年</date>，<placeName key="PL000000015653">歙州</placeName>長史<lb
ed="T" n="0759b02"/><persName key="A010162">許思恭</persName>請往治所。<persName key="A010151">朗</persName>升法座，無何熊伏于<lb
ed="T" n="0759b03"/>前，聞鐘而來，眾散而去。時皆驚懼，虞其搏<lb
ed="T" n="0759b04"/>攫。原其有聽法之心耳，其馴猛獸也若此。<lb
ed="T" n="0759b05"/><date key="j19861681986168" when-iso="+0725-11-04">十三年九月二十一日</date>，告門人曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010151">吾</ref>將去<lb
ed="T" n="0759b06"/>矣。<ref type="person" target="#A010151">吾</ref>三生<ref type="place" target="#PL000000012005">此州</ref>，今一生矣。」言訖，儼然而寂，<lb
ed="T" n="0759b07"/>春秋六十四。稟遺命<anchor xml:id="beg0759003"/>茶<anchor xml:id="end0759003"/>毘建塔。學者既多<lb
ed="T" n="0759b08"/>頴脫，則<placeName key="PL000000011995">開元寺</placeName><persName key="A010172">道飲</persName>、<persName key="A010173">慧祐</persName>、<persName key="A010174">道禪</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000011996">龍興寺</placeName><persName key="A010171">𧦬海</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0759b09"/><placeName key="PL000000011902">寧國寺</placeName><persName key="A010170">進玉</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000013213">越州寶林寺</placeName><persName key="A010169">有沛</persName>、<persName key="A019093">遠整</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000012103">杭州竹<lb
ed="T" n="0759b10"/>林寺</placeName><persName key="A010168">一行</persName>等，並傳<persName key="A010151">朗</persName>之法，相繼若瓜瓞<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1022"/>然。至<lb
ed="T" n="0759b11"/><date from-iso="+0777-02-17" key="j20049012005254" to-iso="+0778-02-05"><name>大曆</name>十二年</date>，<placeName key="PL000000012005">新定</placeName>太守<persName key="A010167">蕭定</persName>述碑，司馬<persName key="A010166">劉長<lb
ed="T" n="0759b12"/>卿</persName>書，刺史<persName key="A010163">李揆</persName>篆額，所謂俱是名公，盛誇全<lb
ed="T" n="0759b13"/>美<anchor xml:id="beg0759004"/>有<anchor xml:id="end0759004"/>矣。</p>
